---
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Str8Positive - Transform Your Life Through Positive Thinking</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Discover the power of positive thinking with Str8PositiveThinking and transform your life with proven techniques, coaching, and community support." />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #f8f9fa;
      background-color: #121212;
    }
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
    header {
      padding: 1rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
    }
    header nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    header a {
      color: #f8f9fa;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    header .logo {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    header .nav-links a {
      margin-left: 1.5rem;
    }
    section {
      padding: 3rem 0;
    }
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .hero p {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto 2rem auto;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 0.25rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0.5rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background-color: #ff3e81;
      color: white;
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      border: 1px solid #666;
      color: #f8f9fa;
    }
    .section-alt {
      background-color: #1e1e1e;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    footer {
      padding: 2rem 0;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #333;
    }
    footer a {
      color: #ff3e81;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <nav>
        <a href="/" class="logo">Str8Positive</a>
        <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="#about">About</a>
          <a href="#services">Services</a>
          <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Transform Your Life With Positive Thinking</h1>
      <p>Discover the power of positive thinking and transform your life with our proven techniques.</p>
      <div>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
        <a href="#about" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="services" class="section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our Services</h2>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
        <div style="background-color: #252525; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.25rem;">
          <h3>Mindset Coaching</h3>
          <p>One-on-one sessions with certified positive thinking coaches.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background-color: #252525; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.25rem;">
          <h3>Wellness Programs</h3>
          <p>Holistic approaches to mental and emotional wellbeing.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background-color: #252525; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.25rem;">
          <h3>Community Support</h3>
          <p>Join our community of positive thinkers for encouragement and friendship.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>About Str8Positive</h2>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
        <div>
          <p>Str8Positive was founded with a simple mission: to help people transform their lives through the power of positive thinking.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Transform negative thinking into positive energy</li>
            <li>Develop resilience and mental strength</li>
            <li>Create a personalized positive thinking practice</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div style="background-color: #1e1e1e; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.25rem; text-align: center;">
          <h3>Our Mission</h3>
          <p>To empower individuals to transform their mindset and achieve their fullest potential through proven positive thinking techniques.</p>
          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">
            <div style="background-color: #252525; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.25rem;">
              <div style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold;">10k+</div>
              <div style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #aaa;">Students</div>
            </div>
            <div style="background-color: #252525; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.25rem;">
              <div style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold;">24</div>
              <div style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #aaa;">Coaches</div>
            </div>
            <div style="background-color: #252525; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.25rem;">
              <div style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold;">8</div>
              <div style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #aaa;">Years</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <div style="max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <form data-form-type="utility" style="background-color: #252525; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.25rem;">
          <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <label for="name" style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required style="width: 100%; padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #444; border-radius: 0.25rem; background-color: #333; color: #f8f9fa;" />
          </div>
          <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <label for="email" style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required style="width: 100%; padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #444; border-radius: 0.25rem; background-color: #333; color: #f8f9fa;" />
          </div>
          <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            <label for="message" style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Message</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" required style="width: 100%; padding: 0.5rem; border: 1px solid #444; border-radius: 0.25rem; background-color: #333; color: #f8f9fa;"></textarea>
          </div>
          <input type="hidden" name="form_name" value="Contact Form" />
          <button type="submit" style="width: 100%; background-color: #ff3e81; color: white; border: none; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; border-radius: 0.25rem; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer;">
            Send Message
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Str8Positive. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #aaa;">
        Built with
        <a href="https://new.website" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">new.website</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <!-- DO NOT REMOVE - Necessary for making visual edits via new.website! -->
  <script src="https://api.new.website/static/new-website.js"></script>
</body>
</html>